law.history: Repealed 1993 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 4, sec. 84, effective September 16, 1993. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 331, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1986. -- Created 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 262, sec. 5.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Guidelines to determine necessity of abstention from voting due to conflict of interest.
